--- title: Chitra keywords: fastai sidebar: home_sidebar summary: "Library for creating data input pipeline in Tensorflow" ---

Install¶

pip install chitra

How to use¶

Loading data for image classification¶

import tensorflow as tf
import chitra
from chitra.dataloader import Clf, show_batch

path = '/Users/aniketmaurya/Pictures/data/train'

clf_dl = Clf()
data = clf_dl.from_folder(path, target_shape=(224, 224))

clf_dl.show_batch(8, figsize=(8,8))

CLASSES ENCODED: {'cat': 0, 'dog': 1}
